HWWI Sees ECB Repo Rate at 2 Percent This Year, Focus Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-10T12:18:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/hwwi-sees-ecb-repo-rate-at-2-percent-this-year-focus-reports.html
Thomas Straubhaar, head of the
Hamburg-based HWWI economic institute, said the  European Central
Bank  is likely to raise the repo rate two to three times this
year to as much as 2 percent,  Focus  magazine reported in a
preview of an article to be published next week.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  